                                        }
                                    ],
                    "body":  "\u003cdiv class=\"govspeak\"\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"eligibility\"\u003eEligibility\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf your organisation has dissolved (no longer exists) or is no longer a trade union or employers’ association, you should ask the CO to remove it from the list.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"definition-of-a-trade-union\"\u003eDefinition of a trade union\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAn organisation is a trade union if:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emost of the members are workers (in most cases this means that they have a UK contract of employment)\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eone of the organisation’s main purposes is the collective regulation of relations between those workers and their employers\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou are also a trade union if:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emost of your members are trade unions\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eyour organisation’s main purposes include the collective regulation of relations between workers and their employers or employers’ associations or the regulation of relations between the constituent organisations\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"definitition-of-an-employers-association\"\u003eDefinitition of an employers’ association\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAn organisation is an employers’ association if: \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emost of your members are employers\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eyour organisation’s main purpose includes the collective regulation of relations with workers or trade unions\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYou are also an employers’ association if:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003emost of your members are affiliated organisations\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eyour organisation’s main purpose includes the collective regulation of relations with workers or trade unions, or the regulation of relations between the affiliated organisations\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"what-you-need-to-provide\"\u003eWhat you need to provide\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eDuring the application process, you will need to provide:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe name of the organisation\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ethe reason for the application\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eevidence that the organisation has dissolved or no longer meets the legal definition\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf an organisation believes it no longer meets the definition of a trade union or an employers’ association, it must provide evidence that this has been agreed by the executive committee of the organisation.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eExamples of evidence you can provide to support your application are:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eminutes of meetings\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003enotices to members\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003ecopies of rules or articles of association\u003c/li\u003e\n  \u003cli\u003eformal correspondence between officials or senior staff\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"how-to-apply\"\u003eHow to apply\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eDownload and fill in the form ‘Application to be removed from the Certification Officer’s list’.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link\"\u003e\n  \u003ca class=\"govuk-link\" href=\"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/65d49df6c2682d001128e8a2/Application_for_Removal.docx\"\u003eApplication for removal\u003c/a\u003e  (\u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003eMS Word Document\u003c/span\u003e, \u003cspan class=\"gem-c-attachment-link__attribute\"\u003e26 KB\u003c/span\u003e)\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGather evidence that the organisation has dissolved or no longer meets the legal definition of a trade union or employers’ association.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eGather evidence that the executive committee of the organisation has approved the application.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eEmail the application form and supporting evidence to \u003ca href=\"mailto:info@certoffice.org\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003einfo@certoffice.org\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"after-you-apply\"\u003eAfter you apply\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eA member of staff in the CO’s team will consider your application and advise the CO on whether to remove the organisation from the list.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf the CO or her team need more information, they will contact you.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf the CO is satisfied that the organisation no longer exists or does not meet the legal definition, she will remove it from the list.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSomebody from the CO’s team will contact you to confirm the CO’s decision.   \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"timeframe\"\u003eTimeframe\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSomeone from the CO’s office will contact you shortly after receiving your application.   \u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eYour application can take much longer if you do not provide the necessary information.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"removal-due-to-ineligibility\"\u003eRemoval due to ineligibility\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe CO can remove your organisation from the list without an application, if she believes that it no longer meets the legal definition of a trade union or employers’ association.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe CO’s team will contact the organisation before the CO makes a decision. The organisation will have an opportunity to explain why it should not be removed from the list.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eIf you are unhappy with the CO’s final decision, you can appeal to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.gov.uk/courts-tribunals/employment-appeal-tribunal\" class=\"govuk-link\"\u003eEmployment Appeal Tribunal\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e",
